## Project Components

### TradingView Library (TradingView License)
- `charting_library_cloned_data/charting_library/` - TradingView's Advanced Charts library
- All files within this directory are subject to TradingView's license

### Application Code (MIT License)
- `src/` - All application source code
- `index.html` - Main application page
- `real-time-test.html` - Testing interface
- `test-websocket-simple.html` - WebSocket testing
- `env.example` - Environment configuration template
- `README.md` - Project documentation
- `README-ENV.md` - Environment configuration guide

## Usage Notes

- The TradingView Charting Library requires proper licensing from TradingView for commercial use
- The application code (MIT licensed) can be freely used, modified, and distributed
- Always comply with TradingView's terms when using their charting library
- This project is for educational and development purposes
